      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NATURALLY BORN (3) was a winner two back when leading throughout but drifted back latest and safely held when 8th and beaten 77 lengths at this track (33.14). Comes out of a solid form race last start. Can discover winning form. SMELL LIKE ROSE (2) doesn't win out of turn. Finished second (28.03) at this track latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Expected to be in this for a long way. DODGY DANNY (4) jumped cleanly last start and led all the way (27.82) at this track in a Novice race over 488m. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. GOOD TOWN (8) did a good job to finish third last time out over 488m at this track (28.07) in a Novice race, the second top-three finish on the trot.",
